description: Secret sharing core library offers implementation of Shamir, Benloh Leichter generalized  access structure using monotone functions, and publicly verifiable secret sharing scheme by Schoenmakers
releaseNotes: Secret sharing core library offers implementation of Shamir, Benloh Leichter generalized  access structure using monotone functions, and publicly verifiable secret sharing scheme by Schoenmakers
summary: In this package three implementations of secret sharing schemes have been provided. These schemes are Shamir, BenalohLeichter, Schoenmakers
